– Internationalization (i18n)

Today's Focus: Multi-language support.
What I Learned:

i18n library setup

Language switching

RTL support

Code:

javascript
import i18n from 'i18next';
i18n.init({
    resources: {
        en: { translation: { welcome: "Welcome" } },
        hi: { translation: { welcome: "स्वागत है" } }
    }
});
console.log(i18n.t('welcome'));
